#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/more_information.rst:2
msgid "More Information"
msgstr "更多信息"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/more_information.rst:4
msgid ""
"That's all the information we have online in our tutorial for the OpenMV "
"Cam for now. Please signup on our `email list <http://eepurl.com/chr-"
"PH>`_ or follow us on `twitter <https://twitter.com/openmvcam>`_ to "
"receive update notifications."
msgstr ""
"目前我们在线教程中提供的关于OpenMV Cam的信息就是这些了。请在我们的 `email list "
"<http://eepurl.com/chr-PH>`_ 上注册或关注我们的 `twitter "
"<https://twitter.com/openmvcam>`_ 以接收更新通知。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/more_information.rst:9
msgid ""
"If you need help please search through our `forums "
"<http://forums.openmv.io/>`_ and if you can't find the answer you need "
"then create an account and ask us. You should get a response to your "
"question in just a few minutes to hours."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要帮助，请搜索我们的 `forums "
"<http://forums.openmv.io/>`_，如果找不到您需要的答案，请创建一个帐户并向我们提问。您应该在几分钟到几个小时内收到对您问题"
"的回复。"
